data.description: This spacious home, situated on 20 acres in Trenton, Florida, features four bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample room both inside and outside. The property includes a sizable 40x60 pole barn, ideal for storing tools and belongings. Enjoy outdoor relaxation on the expansive covered deck/porch or the smaller back deck, perfect for unwinding. For grilling enthusiasts, there's a dedicated patio. The house is equipped with a durable metal roof, capable of withstanding various weather conditions.  Inside, the family room boasts a cozy fireplace, a large kitchen with a separate dining area, and a convenient laundry space leading to the back porch. The bedrooms offer comfort with carpeted floors, and the master bedroom includes a spacious walk-in closet. The master bathroom features double sinks, a shower, and a unique walk-in bathtub. For entertaining guests, a formal living room is available.  The property's well-landscaped yard adds to the charm of this lovely home on 20 pristine acres. The land is utilized for hay production, providing an annual income. Whether for your family or as a long-term investment, this property offers a rare opportunity with buildable land in a county with low taxes. Located between two paved roads, the property ensures easy access without navigating dirt roads. Situated between Trenton, Chiefland, and Fanning Springs, it provides a convenient and desirable location. Contact us today for more details.
